    <body>
        <section name="Run Force Field X">
            <p>One click via Java Web Start.</p>
            <p>            
                <a href="modules/ui/ffx.jnlp">
                    <img src="images/webstart.png" alt="Start FFX"/>
                </a>
            </p>
            <subsection name="Java Web Start Benefits">
                <ul>
                    <li>Full support for Linux, Mac OS X, Solaris and Windows.</li>
                    <li>Full support for 32-Bit and 64-Bit hardware.</li>
                    <li>Automatic download of the required Java Runtime Environment.</li>
                    <li>Automatic download of the required native libraries.</li>
                    <li>Creation of a desktop shortcut to launch Force Field X outside of your browser.</li>
                    <li>Updates of Force Field X are automatic when run standalone from your desktop.</li>
                </ul>
            </subsection>
        </section>
